MUST be done...

1. Automated must be manual.
2. Sortkey must be given for each test case.
3. kiwi test case summary must be exact same as of robot file's test case.
4. plan name must be the robot file name without .robot extension.
5. map the plan name ( robot file name ) and its kiwi plan id inside test_plan.py file.



